{"tid":1760808,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"公廁男女廁格比例不符指引 廁所協會促引入女性尿兜","createTime":"2019-11-28T13:03:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T13:31:43.000Z","uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cc40efefc3ce82ffcf4d298fff9ebf00547ebb95","tid":1760808,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T13:03:57.000Z","msg":"審計署昨日發表新一份審計報告，指截至今年6月，食環署管理的798間公廁中，有138間在過去10年並沒有納入翻新計劃。另外，亦有421間的男女廁格比例不足1比2，不符署方《公廁手冊》指引。香港廁所協會熊志權指，翻新公廁有不同限制，並建議公廁可引入女性尿兜，以縮減女性如廁時間。<br />\n<br />\n熊志權今日在電台節目上表示，翻新公廁有不同限制，並指若翻新工程涉及結構問題需先讓建築師了解情況。另外，若需改善排水系統，更涉及挖路工程，因此需要較長時間審批及改建。另外，對於部分男女廁格比例不足1比2的問題，他則指，建議政府參考歐洲國家的做法，引入女性尿兜，而縮減女性如廁時間。"},{"pid":"19f9422adf2d4dabd44f8492280fd8fcca86fe36","tid":1760808,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T13:06:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2210000/2211760/ce02--_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2210000%2F2211760%2Fce02--_1024.jpg&h=9ea8537c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img4.cache.netease.com/photo/0031/2014-07-22/A1PNR1CH43UD0031.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg4.cache.netease.com%2Fphoto%2F0031%2F2014-07-22%2FA1PNR1CH43UD0031.jpg&h=2b57947e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df24811b40d1cf4e9cbfe52c055f471d11485f74","tid":1760808,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T13:09:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">集會無嘢做？搭緊車好悶？嘆緊冷氣？</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">你哋一直想過嘅人權法過咗啦，仲唔快啲去多謝人？</span></span><br />\n<br />\nTwitter組會24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet like and reply <br />\n㩒入 ----&gt; <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=gSA20A4kU26EBUHkB65AtEy%2FESo4xB68IG1t9wT0pkU%3D&h=49b8d372\" data